    "question_id" : 1686699,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Java does not support this out of box but there is a solution in a form of a compiler plugin and it allows you to do that.</p>\n<p>See this article about id on <a href=\"https://foojay.io/today/operator-overloading-in-java/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://foojay.io/today/operator-overloading-in-java/</a></p>\n<p>Plugin is <a href=\"http://manifold.systems/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://manifold.systems/</a></p>\n"
  } ],
